    <h5 class="w3-center w3-padding-48"><span class="w3-tag w3-wide">Reviews</span></h5>
    <p><span class="w3-tag">Sugar Marmalade (5/5)</span></p>
      <img src="https://www.stephaniewhitetravels.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/sweet-ottawa-4-800x723.jpg" class="w3-image" style="width:100%">
      <p>Sugar Marmalade is a restuarant with the authentic Hong Kong experience. They have a large menu varying from traditional Hong Kong sweet warm soups to classic savoury dishes like tomato pork chops on rice. The endless delicious choices make it an optimal place for any meal. Definitely a 5/5 restaurant!</p>
  		</p>
      
