      <p><span class="w3-tag">The Pickle Barrel (3/5)</span></p>
      <img src="https://www.cbj.ca/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/Pickle_Barrel_921277071.jpg" style="width:100%">
      <p>The Pickle Barrel offers a variety of different Western cuisine. They had a diverse menu which was very impresive. However, there were some problems with the service. It took way to long for my meals to arrive. I also think that for the price I paid, I could get better quality food from other restaurants. Overall, a 3/5 restaurant.</p>
      
