      <p><span class="w3-tag">The Cheesecake Factory (4/5)</span></p>
      <img src="https://img1.mashed.com/img/gallery/what-the-cheesecake-factory-doesnt-want-you-to-know/intro.jpg" style="width:100%">
      <p>At The Cheesecake Factory you can enjoy a great quality meal along with excellent dessert. The service is always spot on and the I can never get over their cheesecake. I always walk out with a full stomack due to their large portion sizes. However, the line up is always long. Overall, a 4/5, definately a great restaurant!</p>
      
